    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a source for parts. The engine struggles to maintain a consistent idle and frequently stalls, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping and delayed engagement. Cosmetically, the body shows heavy wear with several large dents, patches of rust, and faded paint. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and several electronic components are non-functional. It will likely require towing and substantial mechanical work to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 3500.0,
